prodNameC: 協克免疫酵素法退伍軍人菌IgM抗體試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1. Microplate wells coated with antigens:12 microplate strips each containing 8 individual break-off wells in frame 
2. Calibrator (IgM, human)
3. Positive control (IgM, human)
4. Negative control (IgM, human) 
5.Enzyme conjugate: peroxidas-labelled anti-human IgM (goat), 
6. Sample buffer: containing IgG/RF-Absorbent (Anti-human IgG antibody preparation obtained from goat) 
7. Wash buffer: 10x concentrate
8. Chromogen/substrate solution: TMB/H2O2
9. Stop solution: 0.5 M sulphuric acid
10. Test instruction.
11. protocol with target values
